      "title": "Add comprehensive comments and documentation to script files",
      "description": "Per CLAUDE.md mandate: ADD COMPREHENSIVE COMMENTS TO ALL SCRIPT FILES. Review and enhance documentation for all JavaScript/TypeScript files in the scripts/ directory and other utility scripts throughout the project. Add:\n- File header comments explaining purpose and usage\n- Function documentation with parameters and return values\n- Inline comments for complex logic\n- Update outdated or incorrect comments\n- Ensure future developers can understand and maintain the code\n\nAFFECTED FILES:\n- scripts/ directory files\n- Utility scripts throughout the project\n- TaskManager API files\n- Build and configuration scripts\n\nSUCCESS CRITERIA:\n- All script files have comprehensive header comments\n- All functions documented with JSDoc-style comments\n- Complex logic explained with inline comments\n- Comments are accurate and up-to-date",
